都係要頂硬上翻<br />\n平常朝八晚八/九</blockquote><br />\n原來間公司無咗你會執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n份工仲緊要過老母<br />\n做你老母都真係陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係話公司無左你會執<br />\n不過事假係得紅/白<br />\n一係就病假/身體檢查<br />\n病假 事假都係有pay leave<br />\n你請假同事要頂埋你個份<br />\n所以真係請唔到假<br />\n你講得好正確  做我老母真係陰公<br />\n因為香港地翻工仲賤過泥"},{"pid":"f42cd835969d70ccc3552fd4df431c78aa87a554","tid":412322,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:02:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搭單問埋得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老母對腳刺痛  係從肉 從塊皮入面同出黎<br />\n佢去政府睇公立醫院<br />\n話佢神經痛<br />\n開半年藥都無好過<br />\n<br />\n佢今年退休  自己翻大陸睇中醫院<br />\n睇皮膚科又浸又敷都無乜好轉<br />\n<br />\n我預算帶佢在香港睇私家<br />\n但應該睇乜科?皮膚?骨科?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我份工無得請假<br />\n佢自己又唔識唔肯睇私家<br />\n好困擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請病假同佢去睇囉</blockquote><br />\n份工請唔到假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己病都係要頂硬上翻<br />\n平常朝八晚八/九</blockquote><br />\n原來間公司無咗你會執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n份工仲緊要過老母<br />\n做你老母都真係陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係話公司無左你會執<br />\n不過事假係得紅/白<br />\n一係就病假/身體檢查<br />\n病假 事假都係有pay leave<br />\n你請假同事要頂埋你個份<br />\n所以真係請唔到假<br />\n你講得好正確  做我老母真係陰公<br />\n因為香港地翻工仲賤過泥</blockquote><br />\n其實係真係有需要帶阿媽睇醫生先扮病請假啫<br />\n又唔係因為唔想返工扮病<br />\n何況同事請假你都會幫佢手頂<br />\n請一日幾咁閒<br />\n良心過意唔去嘅咪放半日病假<br />\n之後lunchtime即刻返去囉<br />\n<br />\n啲人成日都話返工講金唔講心<br />\n更何況事關老母<br />\n有心嘅點都會諗辦法放假陪佢睇醫生啦<br />\n佢今年退休<br />\n健康好緊要㗎<br />\n順便教埋佢點去<br />\n下次叫佢自己覆診囉<br />\n唔好睇到份工或者自己太重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f91f4b4bc6d705f3237db20048f373b52e2b2aa","tid":412322,"uid":101508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:05:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係關心呀媽嘅，就唔撚好上嚟連登問啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次睇到哩啲post個人都滾滾地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好咁嬲啦 岩岩收工阿媽同我講先知 上黎問下姐 我會盡快同佢睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46790dbb50e09785c0f851d8f0e30c363ac71dd","tid":412322,"uid":101508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:05:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/222704_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F222704_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=95ade90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣？<br />\n痛風嚴重都會關節有粒粒喎<br />\n有無其他症狀？<br />\n不過點都好，快啲搵醫生check清楚啦</blockquote><br />\n似呀巴打 但無咁紅同腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f85daa217fb1e7f6d15c72301403b3c8e290a8","tid":412322,"uid":101508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:06:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快去睇醫生 可能金黃葡萄球菌感染 遲左可能要切手指</blockquote><br />\n堅？？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7fe6e8dd385014a8d5598dadb1ac7fd2744217","tid":412322,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:19:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>快去睇醫生 可能金黃葡萄球菌感染 遲左可能要切手指</blockquote><br />\n堅？？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係畀海鮮拮損<br />\n又無好好處理傷口<br />\n的確好似嗰位巴打所講<br />\n有感染機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0ca4486d430095aace759359f4b8b7c2727e11","tid":412322,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:22:31.000Z","msg":"見到樓上講到份工咁撚